Package com.rb.nonbiz.text.csv

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CsvColumnExtractor<T>
    A simple data class that tells you how to extract a value from a field in a SimpleCsvRow.
    CsvColumnInclusionFilter
    A typesafe thin wrapper around a set of strings to help us specify which CSV columns to bother reading from a file.
    CsvLineSplitter
    Splits a single line of text into comma-separated components, while allowing the possibility of commas being escaped inside doublequotes.
    SimpleCsv
    Represents a CSV file which has been read and loaded into memory.
    SimpleCsvHeaderRow
    Represents the header row (column headers) in a .csv file.
    SimpleCsvParser
    A CSV parser that is simple, in the sense that the entire CSV file is loaded into memory, instead of using a buffered file reader.
    SimpleCsvRow
    A data row from inside a SimpleCsv.
    SimpleCsvRowParser
    Parsing a single row of CSV is simple, in the common case: abc,xyz,123
